<subSubSection id="FF290EAA2FB024A96EC224A618B5FBA7" pageId="null" pageNumber="21" type="description">
<paragraph id="9C976D3E04B2E4365D9BD38B9E084254" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="8CB345293B775BFA319A8C22210B7F5F" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Aconitum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="21" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ranunculifolium">
<emphasis id="A0E3D9D7E675ED923EDC2F583E3D9399" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">A. ranunculifolium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2b) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="E896A454DD49BD5DB460907EF1C294C4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">
<normalizedToken id="107CBCE918FC48E68B8CDB14CE60851F" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
oberseits kahl, unterseits nur auf den Nerven behaart; Abschnitte weniger geteilt und Zipfel breiter, oft kurz zugespitzt, aber nicht stumpf.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="40F7873CEF5F927EEBC271FBCACA3FCA" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A74FF463BA3BE951FE5D2FA50393A23B" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis id="E0B8F8779448494CAEA09CF0815EF36A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Siehe unter Artengruppe.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B134239E5B328A9BF850EABFAC2D4977" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis id="CBD3A89B131B1CA13717388595E536EB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">Standort.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="F4E97D5B1D51D4B35FF4F84FAF6258DA" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Aconitum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="21" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ranunculifolium">
<emphasis id="7231AC1071476CE62D350F0BCCAF7778" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">A. ranunculifolium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2b).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8FFE5DB92BECABC30CDBA607964ACB00" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis id="FDEDA15356F4D1C0106480FCA67E9EEF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">Verbreitung. Alpen-Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="E8B674F8BEC3D5B43440120D9B37FDEE" originalValue="Nördliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">Noerdliche</normalizedToken>
Ketten und 
<normalizedToken id="021320970AF02DBE148F739B55EA48FC" originalValue="südöstliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">suedoestliche</normalizedToken>
Kalkalpen. Verbreitungskarte von Warncke (1964). - Im Gebiet in den 
<normalizedToken id="1ADD843612A35E468BDEE5CF7C609CAB" originalValue="nördlichen" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">noerdlichen</normalizedToken>
Ketten, ziemlich 
<normalizedToken id="8ECE95C5933F4D11C7F46C3B0E93AF77" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8491ED00051862A11802ADFB8EDD64A1" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis id="F00AE5E94731D83F16AB4929CB2CA702" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Von Warncke (1964) wird 
<taxonomicName id="580094D040312D75D9CB609DCEFE3FC0" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Aconitum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="21" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="platanifolium">
<emphasis id="9B8F80FE6015A3E080E4493BE75644EE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">A. platanifolium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
als 
<normalizedToken id="5718DD6C2358CC8ED2A1E25DEAEF6C63" originalValue="Übergangsform" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">Uebergangsform</normalizedToken>
zwischen 
<taxonomicName id="1387C121557CA65D98D753012A550766" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Aconitum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="21" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ranunculifolium">
<emphasis id="1E2DB326D645890011E29BE384B5ABF9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">A. ranunculifolium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
und 
<taxonomicName id="C282B822120E1CB51D67AC9A1F8C98D8" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Aconitum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="21" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vulparia">
<emphasis id="A292F20832FBEAC4C1BB70602879B179" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">A. Vulparia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="15E7CC804DFCA745467E9530D9E187A8" originalValue="aufgefaßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="21">aufgefasst</normalizedToken>
(keine experimentellen Untersuchungen).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
